(39283, 105917, 0, 1, '自由', '', '2011-08-24 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 9, '自由   \r\n\r\n(詞 Noriaki /曲 Ushou)\r\n\r\n那呼吸 已經慢慢的浮現\r\n你卻睜不開眼\r\n\r\n而氣息 已經緩緩的 快凋謝\r\n你卻閉不上眼_\r\nwoo..woo..\r\n\r\n記憶之前\r\n有多久 還沒有 掙脫你自己\r\n那放肆的心\r\n\r\n出世之後\r\n你是否 都沒有 解開了自己\r\n那的狂野的情?\r\n\r\n**自由的靈魂活在 當下之間\r\n深深的悸動 卻看不到痕跡\r\n\r\n自由的蹤影在烙印 你的右臂\r\n綻放精靈 栩栩如生\r\n\r\n-\r\n\r\n假如愛已經慢慢的侵略\r\n你卻沒有防備\r\n\r\n而如今若是 錯過太 多機會\r\n是否想要挽回?\r\nwoo.. woo..\r\n\r\n受困制限\r\n在井底 沒人能 證明你自己\r\n有堅強的心\r\n\r\n癒合之前 \r\n傷口裡 誰又能 釋放出自己\r\n那溫柔的情?\r\n\r\n自由的靈魂活在 當下之間\r\n深深悸動 卻看不到痕跡\r\n\r\n自由的蹤影烙印在 你的 右臂\r\n綻放精靈 栩栩如生 \r\n\r\n(展開華麗翅膀去飛 oh...)\r\n\r\n(solo)\r\n\r\n過去 是迷霧幻影\r\n\r\n像一把尖刀 刺入我的心\r\n歐 愛情 難解的愛情 \r\n我閉上眼睛 回憶 過去\r\n\r\n當她 走入我夢裡\r\n深深的捶入 我靈魂核心\r\noh舊情 習慣了舊情\r\n我很難自由 去飛 遠離\r\n\r\nDo you feel me?\r\nDo you feel me?', '', 471, '', 'Ushou', 'Noriaki', 'Free Road Record', 'Free Road Record', '', 0, 0, 1, '2011-09-30 01:54:48', '2013-10-07 17:19:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(39284, 105917, 0, 4, 'Chromatic', '', '2012-09-15 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 14, 'Chromatic \r\n\r\nLyric: Ushou\r\nSong:  Ushou\r\n\r\nVerse1\r\n\r\nYou should be careful the sun today\r\nit may burn out it anyway\r\ni don''t know what can I say\r\n\r\nI just think it really soon and take me away\r\nnot in that day\r\nso I can fade away\r\n\r\n<Riff>\r\n\r\nVerse2\r\n\r\nI just don''t wanna belive that actually takes\r\nthe destiny drive me away\r\ntake off my guilty with a shade\r\n\r\nSometimes I walk alone on holiday\r\nnothing will be in my life again\r\nbut it still OKay\r\n\r\nChorus:   \r\n\r\nChromatic~\r\n\r\nyou know what I say\r\n\r\nChromatic~\r\n\r\nyou know what I say\r\n\r\n\r\nSolo\r\n\r\nChorusx2\r\n\r\nChromatic~\r\n\r\nyou know what I say\r\n\r\nChromatic~\r\n\r\nyou know what I say', '', 273, '', 'Ushou', 'Ushou', 'Seaman', 'Lizard Blues Studio', '', 0, 0, 1, '2011-09-30 02:24:38', '2013-10-07 17:19:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
